    <item>
      <title>Board</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/library/relationality/domains/universes/semiotic-universe/domains/interactive-semioverse/domains/agential-semioverse/domains/semiotic-project-management/terms/board/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/library/relationality/domains/universes/semiotic-universe/domains/interactive-semioverse/domains/agential-semioverse/domains/semiotic-project-management/terms/board/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;board&lt;/strong&gt; is a projection of the project graph onto lifecycle&#xA;states. It shows how closure flows through the system.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Column&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Contents&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;Closure meaning&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gap&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Predicate graph violations&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Identified but unaddressed&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shaped&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Plans with status: proposed or accepted&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Path to closure is designed&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Active&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Plans with status: active&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Closure in progress&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closed&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Plans with status: completed&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Partial closure achieved&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The board is generated from plan frontmatter by the review-plans&#xA;skill, not maintained by hand.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
